data.title: SATCHEL: Pipeline to search for long-period exoplanet signals
data.name: SATCHEL
data.description: Pipeline to search for long-period exoplanet signals in Kepler time-series data classified on the Planet Hunters website.

evidence: README mentions binaries/installers: "The Kepler stellar catalog contained main sequence stars of many spectral types, but the PH science team prioritized the full classification of the M-type stars after that of the entirety of Qu"
"This pipeline was built for the purpose of finding long-period exoplanet transit signals in Kepler photometric time-series data"
"It has been developed as part of a Ph.D. project... all are subject to editing by Emily Safron, Ph.D. candidate under Dr. Tabetha Boyajian at Louisiana State University."
